article_text:
VIDEO: Sen. Warren calls Donald Trump a 'threat to this country' during Quincy visit

U.S. Sen. Elizabeth Warren amplified her fledgling feud with presidential candidate Donald Trump on Thursday during her visit to the South Cove Community Health Center in North Quincy.
